Ms excel at this exact type of deterministic extraction.\n\n### 4. New Evidence: The Viral Loop Moat\nOQL possesses a massive product advantage missing from every other idea: **an organic distribution loop**. Every time a user generates a \"One Question Left\" poll, they must send the link to their friends to resolve the decision. The product actively markets itself to new users with every single use. \n\nBy building OQL with source-linked verification, we deliver a highly viral, technically feasible, and deeply intuitive product that judges will instantly love.",
